<h1 id="camunda-platform-helm">Camunda Platform Helm</h1>

<p>The Camunda Platform Helm repo contains and hosts Camunda Platform Helm charts.</p>

<p>The charts can be accessed by adding the following Helm repo to your Helm setup:</p>

<div class="language-sh highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>helm repo add camunda https://helm.camunda.io
helm repo update
</code></pre></div></div>

<!-- omit in toc -->
